"elements": {
"075df522-6a99-4c26-a4c8-d8c91fc3975c": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: If you'd cleaned the wound with water or covered it with napkins, it could've introduced different types of infections to the wound.</p>",
"outputs": ["a491a8bb-d7e5-4b61-a845-9284c9b711e8"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"07f149ff-7b50-4a78-be69-d200f2c422e6": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: Hey, the wound is still actively bleeding!!  You don’t want to wash it with water yet, so you don’t need to get water.</p>",
"outputs": ["a5525dc9-1f8b-4e5f-811a-b0db59d6cf78"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"0b751d7e-7752-4c4c-a989-5feca13e5267": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: Just get my bag over there.</p>",
"outputs": ["623f1db5-de80-4339-9c74-ac5e4bdb8a5b"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"0bd61532-189d-44eb-bf38-edfea9672dd9": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: I know, I know, but god, it hurts… so much more now. It's bleeding through the wrappings.</p>",
"outputs": ["0feaa40a-8475-436c-8f4b-a769501737cf"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"0dc8856e-915d-4721-91f1-751ac5a93006": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Frank: Just get my bag over there.</p>",
"outputs": ["0a6ec49c-3a10-4c10-b8ca-b010bf83fe89"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"0ee54dbb-ac8f-47be-a6aa-8c5db6737ada": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>[Name]: What do you normally eat. then?</p>",
"outputs": ["98596f5e-524d-46ec-9e56-13d991a41183"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"126b988e-de6d-4ac7-bb37-8904d96075e1": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": [],
"content": "<p>There is a lot you can do.</p>",
"outputs": ["d69d9bed-8d3b-48f5-b27c-8985bd0e45db", "18797318-5210-4f00-8b57-7993a59d043a", "e6174613-35e3-4cce-ba2c-3a3b51bc077e", "46d3341a-0d74-4438-a282-2ec06090d8e4"],
"theme": "cyan",
"title": null
},
"15fe7685-9090-4750-9192-81ca573d84eb": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["5e87633a-d1f5-40bf-b084-c5220a15ad97"],
"content": "<p><em>You move the chair over to Frank. </em></p>",
"outputs": ["e895a2e7-4927-4713-81ed-15f06cb59c6d"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"1884e9c7-6a24-4fcb-b7f3-d1d0d990e855": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: These gauze rolls, though, should be cleaner.</p>",
"outputs": ["c3f4443f-1cf2-49c9-891b-3ba251ff86e7"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"1d52a7cb-6bc1-4479-a812-bd452ce1d4ad": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": [],
"content": "<p>The timer starts now. you can interact with your phone to call 911.</p>",
"outputs": ["57564ff4-d557-4cc2-949d-854b191debc1"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"2417cc0d-d6fb-46a1-a687-376405f9dab1": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: Alright, can you bring that over here? </p>",
"outputs": ["83325201-efa6-4b0b-95b7-2a65faca6ce5"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"264b7f5f-19ed-431d-b8fe-0512c0850262": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>Frank: Oh, you know, as my training was going on, my parents felt like it’d be better if I got a place closer to the hospital.</p>",
"outputs": ["835a6775-7d3d-4597-ad06-dc419b8609ad"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"2d654f5d-6e4b-4e13-9879-ac83ca6694d0": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>[Name]: ...</p>",
"outputs": ["a8003cc2-63d6-44d1-9862-bb62db0da2e6"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"30611252-18d7-4d79-a1d1-a6244fa38792": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a", "f48f8f8e-9c8c-4bd2-b94f-0228e5832974"],
"content": "<p>Frank: Alright, you’re going to need to wrap the wound. It's a good thing I had those gauze rolls handy.</p>",
"outputs": ["7807c813-5024-4ac3-8953-62528a4a6ddb"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"32767a7c-9281-46ec-b409-e5098882aa0b": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p><strong>Frank: </strong>Oh crap. Okay, it’s important to stay calm and act carefully. </p>",
"outputs": ["f5295702-ff34-4e28-8fd9-bf620d827eaf"],
"theme": "cyan",
"title": "<p>Maya's Invitation</p>"
},
"33352d95-eca8-4f8f-89e1-676ddc632bc7": {
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>You take a deep breath.</em></p>",
"outputs": ["1bb47402-0783-4f77-a918-d028ee335b68"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"35533a31-2b6e-4cf2-9bf9-a904836fc398": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p><strong>You check your phone for the address.</strong></p><p><strong>[Name]: </strong>Alright, on my left… 8, 10… ah. 2012 Chimney Rock Road.</p>",
"outputs": ["b5f4e76d-4c12-4255-bdac-985f24ce0402"],
"theme": "cyan",
"title": "<p>Maya's Invitation</p>"
},
"372748f0-158b-4417-b930-cadd7aba3cbc": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: Be careful with that knife, though. You’re not supposed to remove things when they pierce the skin.</p>",
"outputs": ["2ddce3ab-be48-4167-a55a-42166b8766d0"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"39d35cf1-d157-4104-9e1d-7ea75daa1e42": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: Keeping the knife in actually stops the foot from bleeding out faster.</p>",
"outputs": ["22fb6d27-be24-432b-8702-02756f965ffc"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"3a7710bf-eece-48d9-a816-e66750fcb1d2": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p><em>You get the supplies and unlock the Inventory. You can now access the inventory, seeing the medical supplies as well as your cell phone. You can now go back to Frank, who is now sitting down on the floor, pressing his foot.</em></p>",
"outputs": ["a1dd8c78-e892-4e42-943e-cda1454d65c5"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null
},
"440bfc44-bdc4-47c2-a6a4-5f31afb842a2": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
